The interface "xyz.openbmc_project.Inventory.Item.Chassis.RackMount" is created under paths such as "/xyz/openbmc_project/inventory/system/chassis/Yosemite_4_Chassis" with the ".Type" property set to "RackMount." Meanwhile, the interface "xyz.openbmc_project.Inventory.Item.Chassis.Blade" is created under paths such as "/xyz/openbmc_project/inventory/system/board/Yosemite_4_Sentinel_Dome_T2_with_Retimer_Slot_8" with the ".Type" property set to "Blade."
the interface is just xyz.openbmc_project.Inventory.Item.Chassis
Oh, yeah, we need to create a Item.Chassis with the ChassisType being RackMount.
